summary: Relating to the Drainage and Wastewater Utility; adjusting rates for sewer charges and amending Section 21.28.370 of the Seattle Municipal Code (Section 4 of Ordinance 111425) and adjusting Drainage and Wastewater Utility credits and amending Section 21.76.040 of the Seattle Municipal Code (Section 4 of Ordinance 104472) as of January 1, 1991.
vote: 8-0 in favor of do not pass.
